  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Leetahm atleek/raugi/ tas irr rak-\\stih̅s to Israēta Kehninu Laiku-Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schts bija ta KUNGA Wahrds/ ko wiꞥſch us Jeïfu bijrunnajs/fazzidams: Lihdszet-tortain Augumain tew Behrni fehdehs us Israēta Gohda-Krehf-la/un tas irr ta notizzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Sallums Jabeja Dehls tappe par Kehninu trihsdefmits dewitâ Gaddâ Usijus ta Keh-nina no Juhda/ un waldija wee-nu Mehneft eekſch Samarijas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo Menaëms tas Dehls Gadi/ nahze us augtchu no Tir-zas/ un nahze us Samariju/ un kawe Sallumn Jabeja Deh-lu eekſch Samarijas/ un nokawe to/ un tappe par Kehninu win-na Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kas weht no Sallu-ma Leetahm atleek/ un winna Derriba/ ko wiꞥſch irr darrijs/ raugi/ tas irr rakstihts to Isra-eta Kehninu Laiku-Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad kawe Menaëms Tiw-ju/ un wiſſu/ kas eekſch tahs bt-ja/ ir winna Rohbeschag no Tir-zas/ tapehz ka tee winnam ne bij(Wahrts) atdarrijuſchi/ un wiﬀas gruhtas Seewas wiꞥſch fatappaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihsdefmits dewitâ Gaddâ Asarijus ta Kehnina no Juhda/ tappe Menaëms tas Dehis Gadi par Kehninu pabr Israēlu/(un waldija) defmits Gaddus eekſch Samarijas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch darrija/ kas\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tam KUNGAM ne patifke/ wiꞥſch ne atstahjeſs no Jerobeamma Neebata Dehla Grehkeem/ kas Israēlu grehkoht darrija/ kamehr wiꞥſch dſihwoja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atnahze Wuhls tas Kehninsch no Affirijas prekt to Semint/ un Menaëms dewe Wuhlam tuhſtoſchus Talentus Sudraba/ ka winna Mohka ar winnu buhtu/ ka tas fawa Wal-stiba warreja stiprinatees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Menaëms isspeede to Naudu no Israēta/ un ikkatram Baggatam bijtam Kehninam no Affura par ikkatru Wihrn peez-defmits Sudraba Sihekus doht. Tad greeſahs tas Kehninsch no Affirijas atpukkat/ un ne patif-ke wairs tai Semine.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kas weht no Mena-ema Leetahm atleek/ un wiſſ/ ko wiꞥſch irr darrijs/ tas irr rak-stihts to Kehninu no Israēta Laiku-Grahmata.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Menaëms aisiniſge ar faweem Tehweem/ un Peka-jus winna Dehls tappe par Keh-ninu winna Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Peektadesmiti Gaddâ A-farijus ta Kehnina no Juhda/ tappe Pekajus Menaëma Dehls var Kehninu pabr Israēlu eekſch Samarijas/ un (waldija) diwi Gaddus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un darrija/ kas tam KUNGAM ne patifke/ wiꞥſch ne atstahjeſs no Jerobeamma Nee-bata Dehla Grehkeem/ kas Isra-elu grehkoht darrijs.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
